<font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Donations to help the locked-out workers should be sent (checks payable to the "Alameda Labor Council Hardship Fund") to: Alameda Labor Council, 100 Hegenberger Rd., Suite 150, Oakland, CA 94621<p>
For information on adopting a picket line or other ways to support workers, see the <a href="http://www.alamedalabor.org" target="_blank">Alameda County Central Labor Council</a> Web site.<p>
